ygData.subject: Tolan's Darkwood Bracer
ygData.msgSnippet: Okay this really makes me drool. Where can I find a Tolan s Darkwood Bracer???? Thanks for the info on bows. I love my ranger and am having great fun playing
ygData.messageBody:
Okay this really makes me drool. Where can I find
a Tolan's Darkwood Bracer???? Thanks for the info
on bows. I love my ranger and am having great fun
playing him, and just want him to be awesome. <br>I also
found that if you put a lot of starting pts into
Agility your ranger will get hit way less. I put all my
points into Agility, and with feet like cat and a couple
of Agility rings i paid to have made, I have an
Agility of 160. (I also had a necklace made +7 agility) I
can solo 3 dk blues and only loose two bubs of
health. The mob hits a lot less and on average for only
1-5 pts of dam. (of course you still get hit hard
once in a while)<br><br>just my two
copper<br><br>Mykeal <br>15 Season Ranger<br><br>Murt Morikk<br>21
Season Ranger
